title: Cafe van Gogh
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Mediterranean, Juice bar, Mexican, British, Caribbean, English, Fusion, Middle Eastern
description: A lively (but not overcrowded) vegetarian cafe with plenty of vegan options. Serves breakfast, brunch and lunch offering dishes such as vegan huevos rancheros with scrambled tofu, black beans, salsa, home fries served on sourdough or rye. Some organic juices are available, as is ginger lemonade and coffee.
